From cou.: 1 Correction for ‘Pyroelectric materials and devices for energy harvesting applications’ by C. R. Bowen et al., Energy Environ. Sci., 2014, 7, 3836–3856.
From Soup: 1 The unit of energy density stated in Table 2 (Comparison of operating conditions and energy densities for Olsen type cycles) should be kJ m−3/cycle, and not J m−3/cycle.
 ###### 
From cou.: 2 The unit of energy density stated in Table 2 (Comparison of operating conditions and energy densities for Olsen type cycles) should be kJ m−3/cycle, and not J m−3/cycle.
From Soup: 2 The Royal Society of Chemistry apologises for these errors and any consequent inconvenience to authors and readers.
